snippet.title: Coterminal Angles
snippet.description:
Learn how to find Coterminal Angles in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring. We discuss how to find coterminal angles both in radians and in degrees.

0:03 What are coterminal angles
0:20 How to find coterminal angles
1:01 Example of how to find 1 positive and 1 negative coterminal angle.
